{{Quote|What you have, Senators, is a consensus of fools.|[[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]], to Chief [[Borsk Fey'lya]] and the Military Oversight Committee|<ref name="The New Jedi Order: Star by Star">''[[The New Jedi Order: Star by Star]]''</ref>}}
The '''New Republic Military Oversight Committee''', or '''NRMOC''', was a committee of the [[New Republic Senate/Legends|New Republic Senate]] that attempted to oversee the conduct of the [[New Republic Defense Force/Legends|New Republic Defense Force]] during the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]]. [[Chief of State (New Republic)/Legends|Chief of State]] [[Borsk Fey'lya]] headed it, and [[Viqi Shesh]] and [[Kvarm Jia]] were also members.

